<li>Thinking of you and your family during this sad time.</li>
<li>Your pet held a special place in your hearts, and their memory will live on.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve your loss.</li>
<li>May the loving memories of your pet bring you solace.</li>
<li>We are so sorry for your loss; your pet will be deeply missed.</li>
<li> May your hearts find peace and healing.</li>
<li> Their playful spirit will always be remembered.</li>
<li>Your pet brought so much joy to your family; their memory will be cherished.</li>
<li> Sending love and support during this difficult time.</li>
<li> Know that you are not alone in your grief.</li>
<li> May the memories of your pet bring a smile to your face.</li>
<li>We are here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
<li> Your pet was a special part of your family, and their love will always be felt.</li>
<li> May time heal your broken hearts.</li>
    

